.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, quad-bike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the fan of gospel and the person driving the quad-bike##2
3. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Transport         | helicopter | snowmobile | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

