.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, daisy
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person eating radish and the person driving the car##2
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Flower   | iris      | daisy | orchid   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

