3 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, snake
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the architect is between the owner of the ferret and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Pet         | ferret    | snake | lizard      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

