3 different pets are kept: rat, snake, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Pet         | hamster | snake | rat |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

