.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
3 different games are played: whist, billiard, chess
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person playing chess is between the person watching disaster movies and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Game      | billiard    | chess          | whist |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

