3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the software-developer##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the electrician is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the lawyer is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking milk and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Job   | lawyer        | electrician       | software-developer      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

