.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain, prince
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the car##1
3. the cain-smoker is the person driving the car##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the tram and the cain-smoker##2
6. the prince-smoker is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Cigar       | cain | prince   | aristoff   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 